Dataset : List_of_Orders
Contains order-level information, including Order ID, customer details, order date, state, and city. 
This dataset provides the contextual information required to analyze sales distribution across regions and customers.

Dataset : Order_Details
Contains transaction-level details for each order, including product category, quantity, sales amount, and profit. 
This dataset is used to evaluate sales performance, profitability, and category-wise business insights.

Dataset : Sales_Target
Contains monthly sales targets for different product categories. 
This dataset is used to analyze target trends, identify fluctuations, and compare planned business goals with actual performance.
